'''Savvam Lake''' was an artificial [[lake]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. Lined with genetically-engineered [[Plant/Legends|plants]] and [[Tree/Legends|trees]] that bloomed [[Standard year/Legends|year]] round, it was a place of relaxation for the rich.

The lake was located 200 stories high, sitting atop the roof of many interlocking buildings.

